text: Kan Pisal (born 9 August 1998) is a Cambodian footballer who plays for National Defense Ministry in the Cambodian League. ==Club career== Kan Pisal currently plays for Cambodian League side National Defense Ministry. ==International career== Kan Pisal got his first call-up for the under 23 level team in the 2020 AFC U-23 Championship qualification matches from 22 to 26 March 2019. ==External links== * Kan Pisal at NationalFootballTeams Category:Living people Category:Cambodia international footballers Category:1998 births Category:Association football midfielders Category:Competitors at the 2019 Southeast Asian Games Category:Cambodian footballers
